description.en:
BitBall (BTB) - BitBall (BTB) - All in One Decentralized Cryptocurrency.#NoFakePromises

A unique Multipurpose Digital currency with Endless Possibilities and Rewards - Building Bridge between Digital currencies, Exchanges & Clients all over the world. Our main goals are related to transactions across the globe with a user friendly interface, making it accessible to everyone at every level.. #NoFakePromises.

It will have 2 parts,
1. Exchange of #Cryptocurrency between people with social media profiles.
2. #Ebarter system (historical barter trade between people based on Cryptocurrency). #NoFakePromises.

status_updates.description:
When in Doubt, ZOOM it out 🔍

Since the launch on #Bitmart exchange, #Ballswap has performed better then many other #cryptocurrencies.

Even in this red market #ROI since the launch of #BSP is 2000%.

We thank our community for such great support.

Charts by @CoinMarketCap.

Tweet: https://twitter.com/bitballswap/status/1394156475988074501

After seeing a big demand for #Meme coins & @elonmusk’s interest in the market for #Doge & related #cryptocurrencies.

Would our community like to add a #MEME token similar to #Shiba, #Akita, #Elon to #Bitball Ecosystem?

Early news & access to our subscribers. 

Vote below.

Twitter Voting: https://twitter.com/bitball_erc20/status/1392493865492312065

We are pleased to announce that #BallSwap staking will be available on BitMart #Staking starting from May 12, 2021.

Through @BitMartExchange, every user can stake #BSP & earn up to 70% (APY) BSP rewards.

Tweet: https://twitter.com/BitBallSwap/status/1391021720849436676

English Ann: https://support.bmx.fund/hc/en-us/articles/1260805361129

Chinese Ann: https://support.bmx.fund/hc/zh-cn/articles/1260805361129

To give our community the best out of all #crypto, here’s some of the exciting stuff coming up for #Ballswap.

🚀 Staking.
🚀 Possible new exchange listing.
🚀 89 billion #BSP Burn.
🚀 A BIG 🎁 SURPRISE 🎁
🚀 #NFT Auction Page.
🚀 Banner on a news agency with millions of viewers.

Tweet: https://twitter.com/bitballswap/status/1390224835154829317

Awesome news!

Trading on BitBall #DEX (BitBall-Dex.com) will be available soon.

Trade wallet to wallet with no third party involvement.

Buy/Sell on #Ethereum contract.
Funds are always #Safu. 

Tweet: https://twitter.com/bitballdex/status/1390983235165777920

Attention to all #Ethereum based tokens.

Create pools or new pairs of your #Eth tokens on our #defi platform for free (Blockchain fee applies).

👉 https://app.ballswapper.com/#/create/ETH

Trading of #Ballswap #BSP can be seen here: https://info.ballswapper.com/#/home

Dollar $ value will be updated soon.

Tweet: https://twitter.com/bitballswap/status/1389578110312484866

89 Billion #Ballswap Burn Date Announcement🔥

Our first big burn of #BSP will take place on 
27th May 2021.

Lets all celebrate this event together by sharing the news while we build #NFT page on our #Defi platform Ballswapper.com

Next event: BitMart exchange promotions.
